---
---

<section class="cta-section section section--bg" id="contact">
  <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align: center">
    <span class="section-label">Contact</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">まずはお気軽に<br />ご相談ください</h2>
    <div class="divider divider--center"></div>
    <p class="cta-section__lead">
      不動産の購入・売却・運用など、どんなご相談もお受けしております。<br />
      お電話・メール・フォームからお気軽にご連絡ください。
    </p>

    <div class="contact-cards">
      <!-- 電話 -->
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M8 8 Q8 6 10 6 L16 6 L19 14 L15 17 Q18 23 23 28 L26 24 L34 27 L34 33 Q34 35 32 35 Q16 35 8 8Z" stroke="#1C2B4A" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card__title">お電話でのご相談</div>
        <a href="tel:0368057608" class="contact-card__detail">03-6805-7608</a>
        <div class="contact-card__note">平日 10:00〜18:00</div>
      </div>

      <!-- メール -->
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="4" y="10" width="32" height="22" rx="2" stroke="#1C2B4A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <polyline points="4,10 20,22 36,10" stroke="#B8965A" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card__title">メールでのご相談</div>
        <a href="mailto:yamashita@ptrust-web.com" class="contact-card__detail contact-card__detail--sm">
          yamashita@ptrust-web.com
        </a>
        <div class="contact-card__note">24時間受付</div>
      </div>

      <!-- フォーム -->
      <div class="contact-card contact-card--navy">
        <div class="contact-card__icon contact-card__icon--white" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="6" y="6" width="28" height="28" rx="2" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="28" y2="16" stroke="#D4AF7A" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="21" x2="28" y2="21" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="26" x2="20" y2="26" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card__title contact-card__title--white">フォームから相談</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--gold" style="margin-top: var(--space-xs)">
          無料相談を申し込む
        </a>
        <div class="contact-card__note contact-card__note--light">通常1営業日以内に返信</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section__lead {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-mid);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-card {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
    max-width: 300px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .contact-card--navy {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    border-color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .contact-card__icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-card__title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .contact-card__title--white {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .contact-card__detail {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans-en);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .contact-card__detail--sm {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .contact-card__detail:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .contact-card__note {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .contact-card__note--light {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .contact-cards {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
